    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are consistent with MRL 2 scope and are appropriately documented. The CFD hemolysis model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions in the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under CPB conditions for a Class II device. Submission accepted under ProfileMinimal; the intended-use scope, device class, and operating envelope are described in the Claim (https://uofa.net/morrison/claim/cpb-hemolysis-worst-case) and Requirement (https://uofa.net/morrison/req/cpb-hemolysis-mrl2) nodes.",
